  [2]: https://firebase.google.com/docs/reference/android/com/google/firebase/firestore/Query#count()
  [3]: https://firebase.google.com/docs/functions/callable
  [4]: https://firebase.google.com/docs/functions/callable#call_the_function
  [5]: https://firebase.google.com/docs/reference/admin/node/firebase-admin.auth.baseauth#baseauthgetuserbyphonenumber

